Package: clinicalomicsdbR
Title: Interface with the 'ClinicalOmicsDB' API, Allowing for Easy Data
        Downloading and Importing
Version: 1.0.6
Authors@R: c(
    person("John", "Elizarraras", , "john.elizarraras@bcm.edu", role = c("aut", "ctb")),
